{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9ac1d318c6","title":"利用漫画向党狂猖进攻　徐凡反党面目被揭穿","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"66e53f6f4d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":11,"day":14,"articleId":"9ac1d318c6"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"8bbc7c895e","name":"谭一"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f0f1dca937","type":"title","text":"利用漫画向党狂猖进攻　徐凡反党面目被揭穿","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9ac1d318c6"},{"id":"2492db0575","type":"authors","text":"谭一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9ac1d318c6"},{"id":"fb79ffc6f3","type":"paragraph","text":"《人民日报》讯：湖南工人报总编室副主任兼美术组组长徐凡的右派面目已被揭穿。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9ac1d318c6"},{"id":"11f5ef6246","type":"paragraph","text":"徐凡向党作了一系列的进攻。他诬蔑湖南美术工作“一团糟”。他诬蔑中共湖南省委宣传部文艺处、省文化局和省文联“连本部门的基本任务和职责范围都闹不明确”，他还无耻地叫嚣湖南美术工作者是“没有娘的儿”，煽动美术工作者来一个“庵堂认母”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9ac1d318c6"},{"id":"173191aa1e","type":"paragraph","text":"徐凡长期在报纸上利用漫画作为反党反社会主义的工具。并多方抗拒党的文艺方针。他一直不愿意深入到工农兵中去生活，不愿到火热的斗争中去生活，认为这样会耽误时间，妨碍创作。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9ac1d318c6"},{"id":"f732929f92","type":"paragraph","text":" ——原载《人民日报》1957年11月14日。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9ac1d318c6"}],"page":{"id":"96ab18c422","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9ac1d318c6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}